commit_message:
Optimize building global_declared_variable_set

Use std::unordered_map<>::reserve to allocate memory before inserting
many variables. This improves default config loading performance by
about 23% on my machine:

    Benchmark                                                         Time             CPU      Time Old      Time New       CPU Old       CPU New
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    benchmark_parse_config_json/empty_pvalue                        0.0002          0.0002      U Test, Repetitions: 10 vs 10
    benchmark_parse_config_json/empty_mean                         +0.0102         +0.0102           117           118           117           118
    benchmark_parse_config_json/empty_median                       +0.0098         +0.0098           117           118           117           118

    benchmark_parse_config_json/no_globals_pvalue                   0.0002          0.0002      U Test, Repetitions: 10 vs 10
    benchmark_parse_config_json/no_globals_mean                    +0.0126         +0.0126           123           125           123           125
    benchmark_parse_config_json/no_globals_median                  +0.0115         +0.0115           123           125           123           125

    benchmark_parse_config_json/medium_sized_pvalue                 0.0010          0.0010      U Test, Repetitions: 10 vs 10
    benchmark_parse_config_json/medium_sized_mean                  +0.0160         +0.0160           411           417           410           417
    benchmark_parse_config_json/medium_sized_median                +0.0072         +0.0072           410           413           410           413

    benchmark_config_globals_default_pvalue                         0.0002          0.0002      U Test, Repetitions: 10 vs 10
    benchmark_config_globals_default_mean                          -0.2369         -0.2369         58896         44946         58881         44934
    benchmark_config_globals_default_median                        -0.2348         -0.2348         58891         45064         58875         45053

    benchmark_config_globals_cleared_pvalue                         0.0002          0.0002      U Test, Repetitions: 10 vs 10
    benchmark_config_globals_cleared_mean                          -0.0306         -0.0306            28            27            28            27
    benchmark_config_globals_cleared_median                        -0.0308         -0.0308            28            27            28            27

This commit should not change behavior.
